    <item>
      <title>Child Protection Standards - Wesołe Nutki</title>
      <link>https://riomus.github.io/wesole_nutki/en/child-protection-standards/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Jan 2026 09:28:26 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://riomus.github.io/wesole_nutki/en/child-protection-standards/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;At our preschool, the most important thing is that every child feels safe, happy, and cared for. That&amp;rsquo;s why we implement additional child protection standards that help us care for their safety and well-being. Although these standards stem from applicable legal regulations, they are above all an expression of our responsibility for the children you entrust to us.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Our preschool is a place where every child can develop in an atmosphere of trust, warmth, and respect. We ensure that our teachers are properly prepared and aware of how important it is to protect the youngest.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
